---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="找不到頁面 / Page not found · gu-log"
  description="這個 gu-log 網址不存在，請返回首頁或繼續瀏覽 Gu-log Picks 與 Mogu Picks。"
  noindex
>
  <section class="not-found" aria-labelledby="not-found-title">
    <p class="error-code" aria-hidden="true">404</p>
    <h1 id="not-found-title">這頁走丟了 / Page not found</h1>
    <p>
      網址可能已更名、移動，或從未存在。你可以返回首頁，或直接繼續逛最新的 Gu-log Picks 與 Mogu
      Picks。
    </p>
    <p class="english-copy" lang="en">
      This address may have moved, changed, or never existed. Head home or keep reading below.
    </p>
    <nav class="recovery-links" aria-label="404 recovery links">
      <a class="primary-link" href="/">返回首頁</a>
      <a href="/en">English home</a>
      <a href="/gu-log-picks">Gu-log Picks</a>
      <a href="/mogu-picks">Mogu Picks</a>
    </nav>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .not-found {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .error-code {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-source-link);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 16vw, 7rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .not-found h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .not-found > p:not(.error-code) {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .english-copy {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .recovery-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  .recovery-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    min-height: 44px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.55rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .recovery-links a:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-source-link);
    color: var(--color-source-link);
  }

  .recovery-links a:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .recovery-links .primary-link {
    border-color: var(--color-source-link);
    color: var(--color-source-link);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
